      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">2</infon>
        <offset>56</offset>
        <text>We present evidence for the directed formation of ice by planktonic communities dominated by filamentous diatoms sampled from the ice-covered Laurentian Great Lakes.
</text>
        <annotation id="T1">
          <infon key="brat-id">T1</infon>
