      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">8</infon>
        <offset>1140</offset>
        <text>Bacterial epiphytes are likewise expected to benefit from their association with the diatoms as recipients of organic carbon excreted by their hosts.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1290</offset>
        <text>This novel mechanism illuminates a previously undescribed stage of the life cycle of the meroplanktonic diatoms that bloom in Lake Erie and other Great Lakes during winter and offers a model relevant to aquatic ecosystems having seasonal ice cover around the world.
</text>
      </sentence>
